Privacy Policy
Last updated: 16/09/2024
AYJ SimpleFace ("the App") is a Wear OS watch face application designed to provide a simple and personalized watch face experience. Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how the App handles your data and outlines our refund policy.
1.
Information Collection and Use
The App
does not collect
, store, or transmit any personal or non-personal data. We do not request, gather, or track any information about you, your device, or how you use the App.
2.
Third-Party Services
The App does not use any third-party services, analytics, or advertising platforms. Therefore, no data is shared with third parties.
3.
Children's Privacy
The App does not target children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect any data from users, including those under 13.
4.
Data Security
Since the App does not collect any data, there are no security concerns related to personal information. The App operates solely as a watch face for Wear OS devices.
5.
Refund Policy
The App is a paid application available through the Google Play Store. We comply with Google Play's refund policies as outlined below:
Google Play Refund Window:
Users can request a refund directly through Google Play within
48 hours
of purchase. To request a refund, follow the steps outlined in the
Google Play Help Center
.
After the 48-hour window, refunds are generally not available, but you can still contact us if you experience any technical issues or are unsatisfied with the App. We will do our best to resolve the problem.
For any refund-related inquiries, you can contact us at: ayjapps@gmail.com
6.
Changes to This Privacy and Refund Policy
We may update our Privacy and Refund Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, with an updated date at the top. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any changes.
7.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy or Refund Policy, please contact us at:
ayjapps@gmail.com
